  "original_title": "\u0db4\u0dcf\u0d9a\u0dd2\u0dc3\u0dca\u0dae\u0dcf\u0db1\u0dba\u0dda \u0db8\u0dbb\u0dcf\u0d9c\u0dd9\u0db1 \u0db8\u0dd0\u0dbb\u0dd9\u0db1 \u0db6\u0ddd\u0db8\u0dca\u0db6 \u0db4\u0dca\u200d\u0dbb\u0dc4\u0dcf\u0dbb\u0dba\u0d9a\u0dca",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "A suicide bombing in Pakistan",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "A suicide bombing has hit a convoy of security forces in the North Waziristan district of North-West Pakistan.",
        "Although no security personnel were killed in the attack, at least 10 people were injured.",
        "Also, hospital sources indicate that the condition of three of the injured is serious."
      ],
